          "gameSystem": "nightbane",
          "reference": "Dark Designs (WB6)",
          "pageNumber": 47
        }
      ],
      "description": "The Nightbane is dressed in a hospital gown with a number of tubes and wires attached to the body of the Morphus. Some are identifiable as I.V. lines, catheters, heart monitor leads, etc. There is also an oxygen mask or breathing tube that is easily visible, but the opposite ends of these lines are not attached to any machinery, leaving them dangling or floating in midair. To make things even more eerie, the sound of the missing machinery can still be faintly heard when close to the Nightbane, beeping, whirring, and hissing away. The figure looks gaunt, and somewhat zombie-like with sunken eyes and cheeks, and poor pallor.",
